{"tid":2515210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國電信商Verizon 以50億美元出售Yahoo予私募基金","createTime":"2021-05-03T21:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T00:58:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f72df6caf7986b8d2d0e42a481892b0c95b44bc7","tid":2515210,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T21:52:31.000Z","msg":"美國電信商verizon通訊公司今宣布，將以50億美元（約1398.95億元台幣）價碼向私募股權業者APOLLO全球管理公司出售旗下媒體部門verizon media，此舉將使verizon與Aol.和yahoo!等曾叱咤風雲的網路品牌分道揚鑣。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\nverizon希望拋售媒體資產，轉而聚焦於旗下無線網路和其他網路供應商事業的跡象近來持續增加。verizon去年向BuzzFeed出售《哈芬頓郵報》（HUFFPOST），該公司日前也出售或關閉tumblr和yahoo!answers等其他媒體資產。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210503/4A4QDVKWS5EO3P6FUIHCNF55CQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210503%2F4A4QDVKWS5EO3P6FUIHCNF55CQ%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=d898d627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210503%2F4A4QDVKWS5EO3P6FUIHCNF55CQ%2F&h=4569c049\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210503/4A4QDVKWS5EO3P6FUIHCNF55CQ/</a>"},{"pid":"fbaf9ad7de0323143770cc78676f90a48128d0c5","tid":2515210,"uid":57488,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:42:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<br />\n唔俾tumblr貼咸野<br />\n從此毀滅咗個app"},{"pid":"7d2f31eb3b6069ec90daac7b8872442b18d43872","tid":2515210,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:43:41.000Z","msg":"yahoo點解仲未執"},{"pid":"9364ae1a186977a45a1d6a155218e90925fdd6f9","tid":2515210,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:45:13.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"931d0b1d344f99de2a9b1fa98ca56f0add769e57","tid":2515210,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbaf9ad7de0323143770cc78676f90a48128d0c5","tid":2515210,"uid":57488,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"c